        <body>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <date>(1840)</date>
            </p>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>PHILA.</placeName>
                <date>22<lb/>40 MARCH</date>
            </p>
            <p>DEAR SIR:</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">AT THE TIME I CONVERSED WITH YOU ON THE SUBJECT OF YOUR DISCOURSES,
                I MERELY<lb/> INTENDED TO CONVINCE YOU THAT YOU <sic>WAS</sic> WRONG IN NOT
                NOTIFYING ME (IF NOT AS A <hi rend="underline">FRIEND</hi>)<lb/> AS THE PRESIDENT OF
                THE CONGREGATION. AT THAT TIME, I HAD NOT THE <hi rend="underline">LEAST</hi>
                INTENTION OF<lb/> WITHDRAWING MY ORDER, HOWEVER, I HAVE <hi rend="underline"
                    >RECONSIDERED</hi> THE SUBJECT, AND I THINK I AM NOT<lb/> ALTOGETHER JUSTIFIABLE
                IN DEPRIVING THE CONGREGATION OF THE BENEFIT OF YOUR INSTRUCTION,<lb/> BECAUSE YOU
                CHOOSE TO EVINCE SO MUCH OBSTINACY <del>AND</del> &amp; DISRESEPCT TOWARDS ME, WHICH
                CONDUCT<lb/> (AS MINISTER OF THE CONGREGATION) OUGHT TO BE THE VERY REVERSE; —YOU
                ARE ALSO SETTING<lb/> AN EXAMPLE OF WHICH YOU CONSTANTLY COMPLAIN.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I HAVE ONLY TO SAY THAT I <hi rend="underline">WITHDRAW</hi> MY
                ORDER—NOT THAT I <hi rend="underline">YIELD</hi> IN COMPLIANCE<lb/> TO <hi
                    rend="underline">YOUR WISH</hi>, NOR, THAT I AM CONVINCED THAT WHAT I <hi
                    rend="underline">ASKED</hi> OF YOU AS MY <hi rend="underline">RIGHT</hi> WAS NOT
                MY<lb/> DUE, BUT IN JUSTICE TO OUR CONGREGATION WHO HAVE A CLAIM, <del>AND</del>
                &amp; I TRUST WILL NOT HEREAFTER,<lb/> BE DEPRIVED OF THAT INSTRUCTION WHICH I
                CONSIDER A SIN FOR ANY INDIVIDUAL WHO IS CAPABLE<lb/> OF IMPARTING TO WIHTHOLD. I
                SINCERELY HOPE THAT THIS MAY BE A TERMINATION TO ALL UN-<lb/>PLEASANT FEELINGS ON
                THIS SUBJECT.</p>
            <p>REV<hi rend="sup">d</hi>
                <addressee>I. LEESER</addressee></p>
            <p rend="align(right)">VERY RESPECTFULLY,</p>
            <p rend="align(right)">YOUR FRIEND</p>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <persName role="author">LEWIS ALLEN</persName>
            </p>
        </body>
